  "title": "VETERINARIAN ( Part time -16 HOURS WEEKLY)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Seeking Passionate Animal Lovers and Veterinary Professionals!</strong></p><p>We are looking for  a dedicated Part time Veterinarian - 12 to 16 Hours/ Week. We are an established first opinion small animal practice that prides itself on providing a personable experience for clients and their pets.</p><p>We serve a loyal and affable clientele. You will be joining a team of vets with varying interests and enjoy fantastic support from our veterinary nurses/reception team. No Sunday shifts or afterhours to be worked.</p><p>If you are looking for an opportunity in a<em><strong> low stress and high support environment</strong></em>, this might be perfect for you.</p><ul><li>12 - 16 Hours work week  with  2 sat a month</li><li>Competitive remuneration and commission .</li></ul><p>We see a wide caseload ranging from routine consults, palliative care, prophylactic procedures to emergency medical and surgical cases. The clinic is fully equipped with Idexx suite (Catalyst, Procyte and Sedivue), digital radiography, dental radiography and Midmark dental machine, ultrasound and a user-friendly clinical software.</p><p>We strongly believe in the human-animal bond and want to help our clients achieve the best they can for their pets.</p><p>You should possess a recognised Veterinary degree that is registrable in Singapore with at least 3 years veterinary clinical experience and knowledge of small animal medicine and surgery. Being a good communicator who works well in a team is essential.</p><p><em><strong>What we offer: </strong></em><br /><em><strong>- An attractive salary package - Competitive  hourly rate - $80 to $100 weekday to $150 for Saturday shift</strong></em><br /><em><strong>- Supportive and friendly team</strong></em><br /><em><strong>-Well equipped clinic environment</strong></em></p><p>If you want a friendly place to practice and provide quality animal care, please click to apply or email your CV/resume to manager@ivc.com.sg</p>",
